<h3>Immediate Action (Top 5)</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Fix <code>escapeAttr()</code></strong> — Tambah escape <code>&lt;</code>, <code>&gt;</code>, <code>`</code> — <strong>XSS critical</strong></li>
<li><strong>Tambah <code>maxlength</code></strong> di input nama RSVP — <strong>DoS prevention</strong></li>
<li><strong>Clear polling on logout</strong> — <code>clearInterval</code> di logout handler</li>
<li><strong>Implementasi reCAPTCHA</strong> — atau rate limiting di RSVP form</li>
<li><strong>Bungkus check-in INSERT+UPDATE</strong> dalam satu transaksi atomik</li>
</ol>
